# Client quotation sites

Skill: [`.cursor/skills/client-site-netlify/SKILL.md`](../skills/client-site-netlify/SKILL.md)  
**Catalog:** [`client-sites/README.md`](../../client-sites/README.md)

## Preview showcase

- URL: `https://carlmanuel.com/?preview={slug}`
- Helper: `buildPreviewPortfolioUrl(slug)` in `previewWhitelist.js`
- Embed-only Netlify demos; no “open live site” link in PreviewShowcase

## New client folder

1. Copy `_template/` → `client-sites/{slug}/`
2. Gather brief (Chrome DevTools MCP on Facebook); download assets
3. Customize site; keep Motion + Three.js + embed guards
4. Deploy Netlify; register preview; update catalog README
5. Fill outreach drafts **including** `quotation-followup-3d.md` and `quotation-followup-1w.md`
6. Track state in `client.json` → `outreach`

## Outreach — ask before initial send; hosting cron for follow-ups

| Situation | Agent action |
|-----------|--------------|
| Email found | Prepare drafts; **ask** send now + cadence `3d`/`1w`? |
| User says **send** | `POST https://api.carlmanuel.com/outreachSchedule` (`sendInitial: true`, `autoFollowUp: true`) using `OUTREACH_SECRET` |
| User says **not yet** | Do not call API |
| Offline follow-ups | **Namecheap cron** sends automatically (no Cursor) |
| Pause | `POST /outreachPause` + `outreach.status=paused` |

**Never** auto-send the **initial** quotation without a clear yes. Follow-ups after approval run on hosting.

Secret: hosting `api-carlxaeron/.env` → `OUTREACH_SECRET` (local copy `api-carlxaeron/.outreach_secret`, gitignored). Code: `api-carlxaeron/hosting-php/`.

## Draft files (required)

| File | Use |
|------|-----|
| `quotation-email.md` | Initial proposal |
| `quotation-sms.txt` | SMS |
| `quotation-messenger.txt` | FB Messenger / Viber / Telegram |
| `quotation-followup-3d.md` | ~3-day check-in |
| `quotation-followup-1w.md` | ~1-week check-in |

## Security

- Embed-only + whitelist only; no secrets in `client-sites/`
- Do not add real PII without user approval for demo sites

## Do not

- Auto-send the **initial** quotation without a clear yes
- Commit `OUTREACH_SECRET` / `.outreach_secret` / `.env`
- Skip registering `autoFollowUp` on hosting if user asked for scheduled follow-ups
- Commit Netlify tokens / bypass embed-only guards
